TY  - JOUR
T1  - Case study research on innovation systems: Paradox, dialectical analysis and resolution
AU  - Fragkandreas, Thanos
JO  - Research Policy
VL  - 54
IS  - 1
SP  - 105136
PY  - 2025
DA  - 2025/01/01/
SN  - 0048-7333
